### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Get admin users
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/admin
Accept: application/json

### Get disabled users
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/disabled
Accept: application/json

### Get users by name (replace :name with a real name or part of it)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/username/testuser
Accept: application/json

### Get user by id (replace :id with a real user id)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### Get user and teams by id
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/1?teams
Accept: application/json

